results.occurrenceRemarks: A very large and very nonchalant lizard.  Alternated between sniffing around the picnic ground and sprawling out for naps.  Casually walked up to where I was sitting and came within a few inches of touching my shoe.  Some teenagers left a bunch of scraps behind them, including sausages sizzling on the bbq, which I think is what brought the giant lizard to the yard.
